f galaxies, and the galaxy-galaxy lensing signal\nfrom the Sloan Digital Sky Survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2012 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 26 Jul 2012 20:32:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
